WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.134
which is more
than he needs.

00:00:00.205 --> 00:00:02.537
Brody's got friends
in every town and village

00:00:02.608 --> 00:00:03.836
from here to the Sudan.

00:00:03.909 --> 00:00:06.776
He speaks a dozen languages,
knows every local custom.

00:00:06.845 --> 00:00:08.335
He'll blend in, disappear.

00:00:08.413 --> 00:00:09.971
You'll never see him again.

00:00:10.048 --> 00:00:13.950
With any luck,
he's got the Grail already.

